{"author":{"id":"cff9ab1d2ee9741039b2a60d90cca378a5320ba753398f6f3df8d03abcebee1b"},"ops":[{"type":1,"timestamp":1771236309,"nonce":"SDlpnROSxWPn3o/aCnl9D9rBfcE=","title":"Style Devise mailer templates to match invitation email","message":"The password reset, password change, and email change mailer templates are unstyled English Devise defaults. They should match the styled invitation email template (invitation_instructions.html.erb) which has:\n\n- Full HTML email template with inline CSS\n- MSO/Outlook compatibility\n- Mobile breakpoints\n- German text\n- Bonanza branding and footer links\n- Styled CTA button\n\nFiles to style:\n- app/views/devise/mailer/reset_password_instructions.html.erb\n- app/views/devise/mailer/password_change.html.erb\n- app/views/devise/mailer/email_changed.html.erb\n\nThe reset password email should also include the raw URL (not just the link text) so users can copy-paste it.","files":null}]}